body_html:
I believe the onnx-fb-universe tests are still failing due to a deficiency in the test infra - namely, they continue running again the version of caffe2 without the fix/feature that I pushed earlier today.

I'm confirming this with @bddppq offline, and if so that means we can ignore that failure (I've confirmed that the tests that it claims are failing do pass locally)
